race.comment: SEAMS LOGICAL (7) was heavily supported here on debut and didn't let backers down with a solid victory over the 800m journey. Winning rider Tilley stays on board and has revved up for this with a recent trial win. Likely to take some running down.  I'LLTELLYOUSO (1) is one from one over this course and distance and gets some weight off with the 3kg claim. Top-three aspirations. WARRIOR CHIEF (8) is a bit hit or miss but can feature if she brings her best. HEADLINE LEGEND (2) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be forgotten. Races well over this distance. Scored last time out by 0.7 lengths over 1100m at Gatton and must be included.
